{"tid":1794845,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日男娶初音滿1年  恩愛近況曝光狂曬「老婆照」","createTime":"2019-12-23T12:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T09:40:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"24f585733fdeb478b60dc5fb38e2f04e2edffd67","tid":1794845,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/12/23/phpIQU1Jg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F12%2F23%2FphpIQU1Jg.jpg&h=0ae30893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷自近藤顯彥推特）<br />\n<br />\n日本上班族近藤顯彦在去年11月與心儀虛擬偶像「初音未來」結婚，他常常在推特上分享自己和「老婆」的互動，不斷大曬恩愛。而今年屆滿結婚1週年，正巧逢上新年，因此近藤便與老婆合照印製成賀年卡，將祝福發送給親友。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，近藤顯彦在與初音結婚之後，還特地買了1比1等身大小的初音人偶，而且無時無刻都黏踢踢，他也會在推特上不斷曬恩愛，PO出2人同床共枕、燭光晚餐、溫泉度假等相片，而且近藤也會因應天氣、場合等，幫初音換上適合的服飾。<br />\n<br />\n而近藤也提到，對於現在的婚姻生活非常滿足，儘管目前初音人偶只能透過他自己移動關節，但他對未來科技相當有信心，希望有一天初音能自己動起來與他互動。<br />\n<br />\n近藤對初音的「癡迷」也曾登上外媒報導版面。報導中也提到，今年36歲的近藤顯彥因曾在職場上遭女同事霸凌，所以對現實的女性失去信任，直到初音的出現，她的歌聲救贖近藤，因此才會愛上初音。近藤更相信，他和初音之間有絕對的愛情，初音不會外遇，也不會老去死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/12/23/phpWLOVDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F12%2F23%2FphpWLOVDT.jpg&h=6a5742a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/12/23/phpspQWna.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F12%2F23%2FphpspQWna.jpg&h=c103c990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近藤顯彥也不時在推特上曬出與老婆的恩愛照。（圖擷自近藤顯彥推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3017693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3017693&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwVRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=dfe10727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3017693&h=29ae4e20\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3017693</a>"},{"pid":"183c9786045547021bb049c1893ba4b3aad71ecf","tid":1794845,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"有冇做過愛"},{"pid":"091dd061bb898467719c7ce366a00dd9fece7b4f","tid":1794845,"uid":170595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"毒撚都有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcbc3032b5f3373c30173e4d3a3f2489fdbf29b","tid":1794845,"uid":116704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"183c9786045547021bb049c1893ba4b3aad71ecf","tid":1794845,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"有冇做過愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:30:18.000Z","msg":"唔駛問，點會無"},{"pid":"91dc10bd73367f92faa26fc1479f69dbe0f35a30","tid":1794845,"uid":135408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:31:19.000Z","msg":"你老婆比幾千個毒撚都買左"},{"pid":"4714497b581939918b8dc82ed52de6220399532a","tid":1794845,"uid":122471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"真愛是無價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a378229f5c9be5b537cb2c558d7c62c4a935a46","tid":1794845,"uid":122471,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"好過d仆街連週邊或公仔都冇買過, <br />\n就話乜乜角色係自己老婆, <br />\n仲要季季轉, 年年轉, 1次幾件etc"},{"pid":"d27b89dee6aa00398f0e6a6222b7e7d237d63983","tid":1794845,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:12:51.000Z","msg":"1比1 sex doll?"},{"pid":"72fc71175ddb33e00a841a2a8733badc3c13132c","tid":1794845,"uid":68757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a378229f5c9be5b537cb2c558d7c62c4a935a46","tid":1794845,"uid":122471,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"好過d仆街連週邊或公仔都冇買過, <br